QF Research: 1) NDX rose 20% above its 200D last W.
Since '85 happened 16 times (for the 1st time in M's). Unsurprising often (not always) consolidated or pulled back ST, but 15/16 were up 1Y. Avg 1Y gain = 29.4%?! Momentum is often a thing.
Only exception 2/17/87 (rose 6M then the crash).
